<HEADLINE> Segui Decides To Serve Suspension </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
	TORONTO (AP) -- David Segui will have to wait a day before making  
his debut with the Toronto Blue Jays. 
</P>
<P>
	Acquired on Wednesday from the Seattle Mariners, Segui will  
serve a one-game suspension tonight as the Blue Jays play the 
Detroit Tigers at SkyDome. 
</P>
<P>
	The first baseman received the suspension for his involvement in  
a fight between the Mariners and the Los Angeles Dodgers on July 
11. 
</P>
<P>
	Segui initially appealed the suspension, but has now decided to  
accept it and sit out tonight's game. 
  	   	
</P>
