	ABC's ``This Week'' -- Topics: Deadly office shooting; tax cuts;  
should new laws be passed? Guests: Jimmy Mercer, Henry County, Ga., 
police chief; Rep. Carolyn McCarthy, D-N.Y.; Sen. Jeff Sessions, 
R-Ala.; Sen. John Breaux, D-La.; Sen. Phil Gramm, R-Texas. 

</P>
<P>
                              *------	 

</P>
<P>
	CBS' ``Face the Nation'' -- Topics: Heat wave; tax cuts; Lowell  
Weicker. Guests: Agriculture Secretary Dan Glickman; National 
Oceanic and Atmospheric Administration Administrator D. James 
Baker; Sen. Robert Torricelli, D-N.J.; Sen. Joseph Lieberman, 
