<HEADLINE> AP Corrects JAL's-Battle Story </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
	TOKYO (AP) -- In a story about a possible takeover bid of Japan  
Airlines by its largest individual shareholder, The Associated 
Press erroneously reported on July 26 that Japan Airline's group 
revenues last year were $1.3 billion. 
</P>
<P>
	Japan Airline's group revenues were $13 billion.  

  	   	
