<HEADLINE> Checo Placed on DL by Dodgers </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
	LOS ANGELES (AP) -- Robinson Checo, whose first start following  
his minor league recall was shortened to five innings because of a 
strained groin, was placed on the 15-day disabled list Friday by 
the Los Angeles Dodgers. 
</P>
<P>
	The move is retroactive to Thursday. The Dodgers recalled  
