seven-plus seasons in the minors, where he was 35-43 with a 4.53 
ERA. He was 8-3 with a 4.59 ERA in 20 starts this season at 
Triple-A Albuquerque, and has been in the Dodgers' organization 
since signing with them as a free agent in June 1992. 
  	   	
