shirtless Jevon Kearse stretch out his arms, he thought of a 
pterodactyl. 
</P>
<P>
	Taunted by an assistant coach during a Tennessee Titans minicamp  
drill, Kearse easily outraced his fellow defensive linemen and 
scooped up not just one, but all three cones with one hand. His 
speed left coaches nearly speechless. 
</P>
